item.description:
Genre: Electronic
Style: Trap, Bass Music
Year: 2017
Source: Apple Music

"Ice Cream Truck", also known as "Ice Cream Truck (Impozible Remix)", is a remix by Producer, Artist & DJ Impozible, released in 2017. It is a Trap remix of a tune that is played by many ice cream trucks to attract customers (now some are playing this remix).

Tip: Ice Cream Truck = good food for woofers! ;D
Wish you all an awesome summer!!

Cheers,
ADHDerby
